    "why_vbrick": "FINRA's shift to individual accountability means that compliance officers personally face sanctions if their firm lacks adequate communications capture. Vbrick's Microsoft 365/Teams integration with FINRA-ready archiving provides CCOs with the defensible evidence of comprehensive capture — including video — that protects both the firm and individual compliance officers from personal liability.",
    "outreach_angle": "Lead with FINRA's shift to individual CCO liability: 'FINRA is now barring individuals from the industry for communications failures, not just fining firms.' Ask compliance officers: 'Can you personally certify that every video discussion at your firm is captured, archived, and producible on regulatory demand?' Vbrick's video compliance solution gives CCOs the evidence trail they need to answer yes — protecting themselves personally.",
