    "why_vbrick": "Vbrick's SOC II Type 2 certification, end-to-end encryption, and FINRA-ready archiving position it as a Reg S-P compliant video platform for investment advisers. The platform's security controls satisfy the identity theft prevention and breach notification requirements — and Vbrick's immutable audit trails satisfy the recordkeeping component of the expanded regulation.",
    "outreach_angle": "The Reg S-P compliance deadline for smaller investment advisers hits June 3, 2026 — weeks away. Ask: 'Does your firm's written customer information protection program include your video conferencing platform?' Vbrick's compliance documentation package (SOC II Type 2, encryption certificates, archiving policies) provides the evidence investment advisers need for their Reg S-P program documentation.",
